TESTING INSTRUCTIONS:
1. Navigate to http://localhost:3000/voice-test
2. Click the microphone button
3. Grant microphone permission
4. Say "O, [your command]" (e.g. "O, what is the weather today?")
5. Verify the command appears in the test interface

CHAT INTEGRATION TESTING:
1. Navigate to http://localhost:3000/chat
2. Look for the voice button next to the paperclip icon
3. Click it to enable voice input
4. Say "O, [your question]" 
5. Verify the message is sent automatically

BROWSER SUPPORT:
- Chrome/Edge: Full support (recommended)
- Firefox: Limited support (may require flags)
- Safari: Partial support
- Mobile: Limited support

